title: New NFL superstars in 2015
itunes:title: New NFL superstars in 2015
description:
A room with some heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal and Chris Wesseling -- discuss the latest NFL news including the Bills' quarterback situation, Tom Brady's appeal and the Odell Beckham drama (14:34). The guys then nominate which players will enter and which players will leave the superstar club in 2015 (22:40).

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
